{"ID":270363, "Text":"<div class=\"page\"><div class=\"pageNum\"><a name=\"363\"><\/a><div class=\"prev\"><a href=\"stpjs362.html\">Prev<\/a><\/div><div class=\"next\"><a href=\"stpjs364.html\">Next<\/a><\/div>\n\t\t\t    STPJS 363<\/div>\n  <p class=\"cont\">completed,<span class=\"footRef\">1<\/span> so that men may receive their endowments and be made kings and priests<span class=\"footRef\">2<\/span> unto the Most\n  High God,<span class=\"footRef\">3<\/span> having nothing to do with temporal things, but their whole time will be taken up with\n  things pertaining to the house of God.<span class=\"footRef\">4<\/span> There must, however, be a place built expressly for that\n  purpose, and for men to be baptized for their dead.<span class=\"footRef\">5<\/span> It must be built in this central place;<span class=\"footRef\">6<\/span> for every\n  man who wishes to save his father, mother, brothers, sisters and friends, must go through all the\n  ordinances for each one of them separately, the same as for himself, from baptism to ordination,\n  washing and anointings, and receive all the keys and powers of the Priesthood,<span class=\"footRef\">7<\/span> the same as for\n  himself.<span class=\"footRef\">8<\/span><\/p>\n  <div class=\"topic \">Stakes of Zion<\/div>\n  <p class=\"std\">I have received instructions from the Lord<span class=\"footRef\">9<\/span> that from henceforth wherever Elders of Israel<span class=\"footRef\">10<\/span>\n  shall build up churches<span class=\"footRef\">11<\/span> and branches unto the Lord throughout the States, there shall be a stake of\n  Zion.<span class=\"footRef\">12<\/span> In the great cities, as Boston,<span class=\"footRef\">13<\/span> New York,<span class=\"footRef\">14<\/span> &amp;c., there shall be stakes. It is a glorious\n  proclamation, and I reserved it to the last, and designed it to be understood that this work shall\n  commence after the washings, anointings, and endowments<span class=\"footRef\">15<\/span> have been performed here.<\/p>\n  <p class=\"std\">The Lord has an established law in relation to the matter: there must be a particular spot for the\n  salvation of our dead. I verily believe there will be a place, and hence men who want to save their\n  dead can come and bring their families, do their work by being baptized and attending to the other\n  ordinances for their dead,<span class=\"footRef\">16<\/span> and then may go back again to live and wait till they go to receive their\n  reward.<span class=\"footRef\">17<\/span> I shall leave my brethren to enlarge on this subject; it is my duty to teach the doctrine.<span class=\"footRef\">18<\/span>\n  I would teach it more fully<span class=\"footRef\">19<\/span>&mdash;the spirit is willing but the flesh is weak.<span class=\"footRef\">20<\/span> God is not willing to let\n  me gratify you; but I must teach the Elders, and they should teach you.<span class=\"footRef\">21<\/span> God made Aaron to be the\n  mouthpiece for the children of Israel,<span class=\"footRef\">22<\/span> and He will make me be god to you<span class=\"footRef\">23<\/span> in His stead,<span class=\"footRef\">24<\/span> and the\n  Elders to be mouth for me; and if you don&rsquo;t like it, you must lump it. I have been giving Elder\n  Adams instruction in some principles to speak to you, and if he makes a mistake, I will get up and\n  correct him. (April 8, 1844.) DHC 6:318-320.<\/p>\n  <div class=\"footnotes\">\n    <div class=\"footnote\">1. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115951\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115951)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115951)\">D&amp;C 124:28-35<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">2. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110670\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110670)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110670)\">Rev. 1:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">3. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106020\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106020)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106020)\">Gen. 14:22<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">4. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106059\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106059)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106059)\">Gen. 28:17<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114918\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114918)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114918)\">D&amp;C 88:119<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116704\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116704)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116704)\">D&amp;C 138:58<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">5. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115960\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115960)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115960)\">D&amp;C 124:29-36,39<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">6. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114055\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114055)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114055)\">D&amp;C 57:3<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">7. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116139\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116139)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116139)\">D&amp;C 128:11<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116426\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116426)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116426)\">D&amp;C 132:45,59<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">8. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116705\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116705)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116705)\">D&amp;C 138:58<\/a><\/span