:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(117141)\">JS&mdash;H 1:63-64<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115981\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115981)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115981)\">D&amp;C 124:39<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115942\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115942)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115942)\">D&amp;C 124:27-42<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">17. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"109921\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 109921)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(109921)\">Col. 3:24<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"110632\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 110632)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(110632)\">2 Jn. 1:8<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112303\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112303)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112303)\">Alma 41:14<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"114116\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 114116)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(114116)\">D&amp;C 59:3,23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"116712\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 116712)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(116712)\">D&amp;C 138:59<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">18. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113118\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113118)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113118)\">D&amp;C 5:10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113370\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113370)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113370)\">D&amp;C 20:38,42,68<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"113425\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 113425)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(113425)\">D&amp;C 23:3,5<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"115518\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 115518)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(115518)\">D&amp;C 107:91-92,99<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">19. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111052\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111052)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111052)\">1 Ne. 19:23<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111766\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111766)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111766)\">Alma 4:4<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">20. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108264\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108264)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108264)\">Matt. 26:41<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108369\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108369)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108369)\">Mark 14:38<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">21. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106103\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106103)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106103)\">Ex. 4:14-16<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106182\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106182)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106182)\">Ex. 24:1,9-10<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"106244\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 106244)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(106244)\">Num. 11:16,24-25<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"